1
00:00:01,415 --> 00:00:05,713
What are you going to do with that vase, Penny?
你打算如何处理那花瓶, Penny?

2
00:00:06,803 --> 00:00:10,472
I'm going to put it on this table, Sam.
我打算把它放在这张桌子上, Sam.

3
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:12,770
Don't do that.
不要放在那儿.

4
00:00:13,958 --> 00:00:15,246
Give it to me.
把它给我.

5
00:00:16,629 --> 00:00:18,970
What are you going to do with it?
你打算怎么办?

6
00:00:20,207 --> 00:00:25,272
I'm going to put it here, in front of the window.
我准备把它放在这儿, 放在窗前.

7
00:00:26,140 --> 00:00:27,374
Be careful!
小心点!

8
00:00:28,199 --> 00:00:29,526
Don't drop it!
别摔了!

9
00:00:30,888 --> 00:00:32,938
Don't put it there, Sam.
别放在那儿, Sam.

10
00:00:34,357 --> 00:00:37,388
Put it here, on this shelf.
放在这儿, 这个架子上.

11
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:43,382
There we are! It's a lovely vase.
就这样! 这是只漂亮的花瓶.

12
00:00:44,416 --> 00:00:47,446
Those flowers are lovely, too.
那些花也很漂亮啊.

